data.description: Luxury Living in McDonough's Heart! This exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence is a true gem, ideally situated just minutes from the McDonough square, where you can indulge in a plethora of shops and restaurants. Nestled on a meticulously landscaped lot, this home exudes elegance and comfort. As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by the timeless allure of plantation shutters that grace each window, allowing natural light to fill every room. The spacious living areas are perfect for both relaxation and entertaining, with a tastefully designed layout that seamlessly flows from room to room. The heart of this home is undoubtedly its large, gourmet kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream come true. It boasts top-of-the-line appliances, ample counter space, and top of the line cabinetry, making it a haven for those who love to cook and gather with loved one. In the evenings, retreat to your luxurious master suite, complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom, two oversized walk-in closets and a sitting room. Four additional generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or even a home office. Step outside to discover your own private oasis. The large screened-in porch is an ideal spot to enjoy the serene views of your fully landscaped yard, which is perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings. This magnificent home offers the finest in luxury living and convenience, making it a must-see property in McDonough. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home and experience the epitome of comfort and style. Schedule your private tour today!
